<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-3YOtroFactor" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>9: I just knew it. I know <m>2 \times 3</m> is 6, and 3 more is 9.</li>
      <li>21: Six times 3 is twice 3 times 3, which is <m>2 \times 9</m> or 18. Adding 3 more gives 21.</li>
      <li>30: I know that <m>3 \times 10</m> is 30 and <m>10 \times 3</m> is also 30. I just knew it.</li>
      <li>51: It’s the sum of <m>10 \times 3</m> and <m>7 \times 3</m>, which I know is 30 and 21. I know <m>3 \times 20</m> is 60 and <m>3 \times 17</m> is <m>3 \times 3</m> less than 60 or <m>60 - 9</m>, which is 51. </li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


